Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.16,0:42:54.01,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We stretch our small, dream bearing wings in the summer sky
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.34,0:43:07.73,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Chasing a wind that flows between the clouds, we begin to walk
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.73,0:43:16.24,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You spoke of tomorrow, under the hot rays of the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.70,0:43:26.71,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As your eyes stared at and longed for a sky so very far away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.63,0:43:37.14,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now we are still searching
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.26,0:43:43.60,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For that ladder we spoke of and aimed for when we were young
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.60,0:43:50.61,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We look up at and chase after the flowing stardust
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.36,0:43:57.74,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Vestiges of the future remain in our outstretched hands
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.99,0:44:06.46,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As the two of us wait for the night to finally break
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.80,0:44:28.10,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The path I used to walk alone is now shared with you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.69,0:44:42.28,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Our song, shimmering in the starry summer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.69,0:44:42.28,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sky, is heard throughout the world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.91,0:44:50.25,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Passed down by the stars like an ancient hero
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.75,0:44:56.26,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even the far-off distant sky
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.63,0:45:01.47,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Is only a short distance away
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.60,0:45:11.06,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now we are still performing it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.52,0:45:17.40,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In a gentle voice that envelops this cradle
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.40,0:45:25.16,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I swear upon the shining stardust
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.29,0:45:31.75,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I will overtake it, without hesitating or giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.96,0:45:39.55,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And go down the same path with you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.91,0:46:15.25,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now we are still chasing it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.71,0:46:22.34,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That flame on a journey to a distant world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.47,0:46:31.06,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now we are still watching over it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.31,0:46:37.44,ED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As the future is in our view
